globalEvents.title: BRIEFING
globalEvents.message: Titan-class Terminid eggs recently sold as patriotic curios to Class-A citizensdemonstrably the top 1% of patriots within the Federationhave experienced unauthorized biological activation. Bizarrely coinciding with this phenomenon, Terminids are ransacking high-density Class-A citizen zones. Reports of "coordinated" Terminids are officially attributed to pheromones emitted by the hatchlings, and nothing more. Spotless urban centers of planets like Polaris Prime are being befouled both by hatching vermin, and the fully-grown fascist swarm, as it belligerently destroys everything in its path. This aggressive trespassing threatens shareholder value, domestic tranquility, and workforce productivity. The strategic expenditure of addressing Cyborg Tyranny on Cyberstan requires High Command to temporarily tighten the Belt of Liberty. Under restricted operational parameters, reinforcement budgets are strictly limited, and shortfalls in the supply of Stims and ammunition should be expected. True heroes, however, require little more than moral superiority to slaughter monsters. To repel this grotesque swarm, stabilize the frontlines, and halt the Terminid advance, Helldivers are ordered to liberate more planets than are lost.
